00:38:28,692 --> 00:38:30,650
Nobody goes off-trail.

380
00:38:30,733 --> 00:38:32,192
And nobody walks alone.

381
00:38:33,192 --> 00:38:34,567
Nobody goes off-trail.

382
00:38:34,650 --> 00:38:37,400
- So it's not better.
- And nobody walks alone.

383
